commitResults.messageBody:
The Goods class currently lacks the necessary CsvBinds for proper CSV
serialization and deserialization.

Add CsvConverters for custom types and apply CsvBinds to the Goods class
 fields.

This change ensures that the Goods class can be correctly serialized and
 deserialized using OpenCSV.
